creditline: Gift of funds from Mary and Bob Mersky
dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: Protect yourself and those around you. The disconnect between the spring awakening and the grief for the world in turmoil is palpable. Do you feel it too?
title: April 26, 2020: THERE IS NO IMMUNITY.
